Freedom of Information Act (FOIA)

   Welcome to the NARA Freedom of Information Act (FOIA) Homepage.
     * Access Guide
       This Guide provides instructions on obtaining information from
       NARA, several links to information and/or documents that may be
       useful to you, and lists of NARA facilities and their addresses.

     * NARA FOIA Liaisons
       List of NARA FOIA contacts including: name, address, telephone
       number, and fax number.

     * FOIA Annual Reports

     * FOIA Annual Report - 1996
     * FOIA Annual Report - 1997
     * FOIA Annual Report - 1998
     * FOIA Annual Report - 1999
     * FOIA Annual Report - 2000


     Electronic Reading Room New
   This site contains information routinely available to the public as
   well as documents frequently requested under the Freedom of Information
   Act. The page will continue to grow as we add records in which the
   public expresses an interest.



