     Other FOIA Resources

     * DEPARTMENT OF JUSTICE FOIA HOMEPAGE
       The Department of Justice FOIA page contains a list of Principle
       FOIA Contacts at other agencies, the text of the FOIA, Privacy Act,
       FOIA UPDATE, and the FOIA POST.

